"JVM fast-jar, JVM with xref:aot.adoc[Project Leyden AOT caching] (JDK 24+), and native (Mandrel) each trade cold-start speed, peak throughput, memory footprint, and build cost differently.\n"
"The table below compares them.\n"
"Pick the mode that matches your workload's most important constraint."
msgstr ""

